      <section eId="sec_723">
        <num>723</num>
        <heading>Penalties for violation of this article</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_723__subsec_i">
          <num>(i)</num>
          <content>
            <p>two\nthousand dollars or where such violation is willful ten thousand dollars\nfor each offense; (ii) a multiple of two times the aggregate damages\nattributable to the violation; or (iii) a multiple of two times the\naggregate economic gain attributable to the violation.\n  2. Nothing in this article shall limit any statutory or common-law\nright of any person to bring any action in any court for any act, or the\nright of the state to punish any person for any violation of any law.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
